Class OMAGOIFAPIResponse

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.commonservices.ffdc.rest.FFDCResponseBase
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworkservices.oif.rest.OMAGOIFAPIResponse
All Implemented Interfaces:
FFDCResponse
Direct Known Subclasses:
IntegrationReportResponse, IntegrationReportsResponse
public abstract class OMAGOIFAPIResponse extends FFDCResponseBase
OMAGOIFAPIResponse provides a common header for Metadata Store Service managed rest to its REST API. It manages information about exceptions. If no exception has been raised exceptionClassName is null.
